    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "bf0763f69d9c9bac60b5487de9b690e0",
      "text": "Under the Commons Act 1876 some 36 commons in England and Wales were regulated. The act also enabled the confirmation of Orders providing for the inclosure of common land or common fields and butts"
    },
