      "id": "bba2f75ed172db1a565e322ba51d6908",
      "text": "This includes a description of the rights of common (e.g. a right to graze a certain amount of sheep), the area of common over which the right is exercisable, the name of the holder of the right and whether the right is attached to land in the ownership of the holder of the right (the commoner) or is a right held in gross i.e. unattached to land."
    },
